<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script>
  $(function() {
    $("p").on({
      mouseenter: function() {
        $(this).css("background-color", "yellow");
      },
      mouseleave: function() {
        $(this).css("background-color", "blue");
      },
      click: function() {
        $(this).css("background-color", "red");
      }
    });
  });
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>jQuery event</h1>
  <p>안녕하세요. 데브쿠마입니다.</p>
</body>
</html>